                      to amazing amenities.”
                    </p>
                    <h6 class="mb-0 fw-semibold text-muted">— Anita K.</h6>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <a href="/theme/2/testimonials" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary">
                Read More Testimonials <i class="ri-arrow-right-line ms-2"></i>
              </a>
            </div>
